caption:
Punjabi superstar Ammy Virk lit up the red carpet at the exclusive Dubai premiere of Sarbala Ji, hosted by Ankur Aggarwal and BNW Developments at VOX Cinemas, Nakheel Mall.

An unforgettable night celebrating cinema, culture, and cross-border storytelling 🎬
@ankur.aggarwal01 
@ammyvirk 
@bnw.developments @sargunmehta 
@vivekoberoi 
@naresh_golapalli 

#SarbalaJi #AmmyVirk #BNWDevelopments #AnkurAggarwal #DubaiPremiere #PunjabiCinema #RedCarpetDubai #DesiVibesInDubai #VOXCinemas

🎬✨ Dubai goes Desi in style! As Mr. Ankur Aggarwal, Chairman & Founder of BNW Developments rolled out the red carpet for the exclusive premiere of Sarbala Ji, with none other than Punjabi superstar Ammy Virk stealing the spotlight 🌟

Held at VOX Cinemas, Nakheel Mall, this invite-only night brought together cinema, culture & community, as Ammy connected with fans ahead of the global release. A true celebration of storytelling without borders 🇦🇪🇮🇳

